org.digijava.module.translation.exotic

Class ExoticMonthNames

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.digijava.module.translation.exotic.ExoticMonthNames

  • public class ExoticMonthNames
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing month names with locales unsupported by Java 8. To add a new one, create a file ExoticMonthNames_{two-letter-code}.properties in this package. Originally created for Tetum (Timor).
